description: This is a course for High School students who would like to improve their SAT Math score. This course was developed for students who feel that they are trying as much as they can but still can't see an improvement in their SAT Math score. This course is designed for the student to analyze the gap and thereby improve their score.
title: Double your SAT Math score in a week
instructors: Raman Perumal, Vigneshwar Perumal, Sridevi Perumal, Nivashini Muthuvel
